---
description: Backend API route guidance
globs:
    - "src/app/api/**/*"
    - "src/services/**/*"
alwaysApply: false
---

Validate every request boundary, return JSON-safe payloads, avoid stack/secret
leaks, gate privileged routes with server-only secrets, and keep external calls
bounded and observable. Prefer existing Next.js route patterns, viem clients,
and service helpers over new dependencies.
